{"about_the_game":"Hive Quest is an immersive real time strategy game set in a mythical woodland filled with ancient magic, strange creatures &amp; intriguing puzzles. As the Hive Mind you will guide your insect tribe on a hazardous adventure to find safety after a terrible cataclysm. Explore mysterious locations with the help of your pet Shrublet, find allies, uncover the story behind the Old Orchard and fight against other tribes. Do you have what it takes to re-establish your Hive\u2019s fortunes and seek out the mythical \u2018Sunny Uplands\u2019?<br><br>\u2013 Guide your embattled tribe on a quest to find fortune, glory and a new home.<br>\u2013 Interact with a wide variety of crazy puzzles and strange goings on as you try to make sense of it all.<br>\u2013 Explore the mysteries of the Deep Woods and uncover new allies and enemies.<br>\u2013 Battle against other hives to maintain control of your territory.<br>\u2013 Manage resources and build your Hive into a powerful kingdom, filled with hard working drones.<br>\u2013 Take mind control of your drones and send them into unknown territory on dangerous missions.<br>\u2013 Launch attacks on enemy Hives &amp; dangerous creatures that stand in your way.<br>\u2013 Obtain woodland elementals as pets and upgrade them to fight and do your bidding.<br><br>Thanks for looking!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/843280/extras/n1.png?t=1680360566\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/843280/extras/n6.png?t=1680360566\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/843280/extras/n2.png?t=1680360566\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/843280/extras/n5.png?t=1680360566\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/ste